#: ../../../platforms/plugin.md:80
msgid ""
"load_plugins()\n"
"  ├── _get_excluded_dists()                       → compute dists to skip "
"(via SGLANG_PLATFORM)\n"
"  ├── load_plugins_by_group(\"sglang.srt.plugins\",     → discover "
"entry_points, filter by SGLANG_PLUGINS\n"
"  │     excluded_dists=...)                          skip plugins from "
"unselected platform packages\n"
"  ├── for each plugin:                            → set "
"_current_plugin_source context var\n"
"  │     func()                                      side effects (register "
"hooks with source tracking)\n"
"  └── HookRegistry.apply_hooks()                  → monkey-patch targets\n"
msgstr ""

